PN,41701
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,FThere have been calls for a different
OL,7,Forganisation to carry out a review for
OL,8,Fthe DUP into what was known about
OL,9,FJeffrey Donaldson prior to his
OL,10,Fconviction for child sex abuse.
OL,12,FCampaign groups are concerned there
OL,13,Fwill be a potential conflict of
OL,14,Finterest, as the safeguarding group
OL,15,FiNEQE, led by former police officer
OL,16,FJim Gamble is also conducting a
OL,17,Fseparate review into safeguarding
OL,18,Fconcerns in the Presbyterian Church of
OL,19,FIreland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,FVictims of Donaldson disclosed their
OL,7,Fabuse to the church.
OL,9,FMarcella Leonard, safeguarding expert
OL,10,Fand spokesperson for the Northern
OL,11,FIreland Survivor Council (NISC), has
OL,12,Fsaid that they believe the
OL,13,Forganisation covering both the
OL,14,FDonaldson review and the Presbyterian
OL,15,FChurch safeguarding review does not
OL,16,Fhave sufficient independence to carry
OL,17,Fout both cases simultaneously, leading
OL,18,Fto a "blurring" of information between
OL,19,Fcases.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,FMs Leonard told UTV that there could
OL,7,Fbe "cross-referencing of information,
OL,8,Fthere's going to be seeping of
OL,9,Fknowledge from one review into the
OL,10,Fother".
OL,12,FShe continued: "At this stage, my
OL,13,Fadvice would be, you need to have two
OL,14,Fvery separate independent reviews.
OL,15,FThen their findings can be collated at
OL,16,Fthe end. This is not about making an
OL,17,Fopinion on whether or not somebody's
OL,18,Fcapable, it's about what is right, and
OL,19,Fwhat is right is having a clear
OL,20,Findependent review."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,FJim Gamble, the lead reviewer, has
OL,7,Fbeen reported as saying his priority
OL,8,Fis to hear the victims, provide
OL,9,Fanswers to their questions and explain
OL,10,Fsafeguards they use to ensure they are
OL,11,Frigorous and independent. He has
OL,12,Foffered to meet with the Survivors
OL,13,FCouncil.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,FUTV contacted the DUP for comment, but
OL,7,Fthe party pointed to an earlier
OL,8,Fstatement: "The DUP has commissioned
OL,9,Fthe iNEQE Safeguarding Group to
OL,10,Fconduct an Independent Focused
OL,11,FSafeguarding Review for the Democratic
OL,12,FUnionist Party into Jeffrey
OL,13,FDonaldson's time as a member of the
OL,14,FParty.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"The DUP has commissioned this focused
OL,7,Findependent review to establish what,
OL,8,Fif any, information was known within
OL,9,Fthe Party about his conduct, to
OL,10,Fexamine its safeguarding and reporting
OL,11,Farrangements, and to make
OL,12,Frecommendations to ensure good
OL,13,Fpractice for all its members and staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"The review will be carried out by a
OL,7,Fspecialist multi-disciplinary team
OL,8,Ffrom the iNEQE Safeguarding Group,
OL,9,Fdrawing on their safeguarding, child
OL,10,Fprotection and policing expertise. The
OL,11,Freview will be led by Mr Jim Gamble.
OL,12,FThe review will be conducted entirely
OL,13,Findependent of the DUP.
OL,15,F"The terms of reference for the review
OL,16,Fwill be;
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"Conduct an independent review to
OL,7,Festablish what (if any) information
OL,8,Fwas known within the DUP concerning
OL,9,Fallegations of inappropriate conduct
OL,10,Frelating to safeguarding by Jeffrey
OL,11,FDonaldson. This will include who knew,
OL,12,Fwhen and from whom they learned it,
OL,13,Fthe form in which it arose
OL,14,F(eyewitness, formal complaint,
OL,15,Fdisclosure, concern, rumour or
OL,16,Fwarning), and what action was or was
OL,17,Fnot taken.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"Provide an independent and
OL,7,Fconfidential facility for party
OL,8,Fmembers to come forward with related
OL,9,Finformation, concerns or experiences
OL,10,Frelating to Jeffrey Donaldson during
OL,11,Fhis time in the DUP.
OL,13,F"Examine and review the DUP's
OL,14,Fsafeguarding processes (including
OL,15,Freporting mechanisms) and make
OL,16,Frecommendations to ensure good
OL,17,Fpractice is followed by all members
OL,18,Fand staff.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"Full terms of reference will be
OL,7,Fpublished by iNEQE when they launch
OL,8,Ftheir website for this review.
OL,10,F"The DUP acted immediately when
OL,11,FJeffrey Donaldson was first charged.
OL,12,FWe believe in the rule of law and that
OL,13,Fjustice must be obtained through our
OL,14,Fcourts. We stand with the victims of
OL,15,Fhis abuse and we salute their bravery
OL,16,Fand courage for speaking out.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"Regardless of the crime, we will
OL,7,Falways be on the side of the victim
OL,8,Fand as a society, we must do
OL,9,Feverything possible to encourage those
OL,10,Fwho have been abused to come forward
OL,11,Fto the police and seek justice through
OL,12,Four court system.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41712
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"As a consequence of his actions,
OL,7,FJeffrey Donaldson must now feel the
OL,8,Ffull force of the law. He stands
OL,9,Fguilty of abusing and betraying the
OL,10,Ftrust placed in him by many people
OL,11,Fover the years, including good honest
OL,12,Fcolleagues in both our party and the
OL,13,FUlster Unionist Party as well as the
OL,14,Fwider community.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,418,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41713
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F417A1784233114
OL,3,CConcern over DUP review 'conflict of
OL,4,Cinterest'
OL,6,F"While the DUP never received any
OL,7,Freport or complaint regarding improper
OL,8,Fbehaviour or criminal behaviour, it is
OL,9,Fnow clear, beyond doubt, that Jeffrey
OL,10,FDonaldson abused various positions of
OL,11,Fpower over many years from 1985
OL,12,Fonwards and covered up his vile and
OL,13,Fmanipulative behaviour.
OL,15,F"The work of the review has now
OL,16,Fcommenced and the Party does not
OL,17,Fintend to give a running commentary on
OL,18,Fit whilst it is ongoing respecting the
OL,19,Ffundamental independent nature of it."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
